<p><a name="See_also" id="See_also"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Grigori_Perelman&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: See also">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">See also</span></h2>
