ki/David_Mumford" title="David Mumford">David Mumford</a> (1974)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Pierre_Deligne" title="Pierre Deligne">Pierre Deligne</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Charles_Fefferman" title="Charles Fefferman">Charles Fefferman</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Grigory_Margulis" title="Grigory Margulis">Grigory Margulis</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Daniel_Quillen" title="Daniel Quillen">Daniel Quillen</a> (1978)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Alain_Connes" title="Alain Connes">Alain Connes</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/William_Thurston" title="William Thurston">William Thurston</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Shing-Tung_Yau" title="Shing-Tung Yau">Shing-Tung Yau</a> (1982)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Simon_Donaldson" title="Simon Donaldson">Simon Donaldson</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Gerd_Faltings" title="Gerd Faltings">Gerd Faltings</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Michael_Freedman" title="Michael Freedman">Michael Freedman</a> (1986)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Vladimir_Drinfel%27d" title="Vladimir Drinfel'd">Vladimir Drinfel'd</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Vaughan_Jones" title="Vaughan Jones">Vaughan Jones</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Shigefumi_Mori" title="Shigefumi Mori">Shigefumi Mori</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Edward_Witten" title="Edward Witten">Edward Witten</a> (1990)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Efim_Zelmanov" title="Efim Zelmanov">Efim Zelmanov</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Pierre-Louis_Lions" title="Pierre-Louis Lions">Pierre-Louis Lions</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Jean_Bourgain" title="Jean Bourgain">Jean Bourgain</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Jean-Christophe_Yoccoz" title="Jean-Christophe Yoccoz">Jean-Christophe Yoccoz</a> (1994)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Richard_Borcherds" title="Richard Borcherds">Richard Borcherds</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/William_